1
00:00:18,870 --> 00:00:19,800
What is this for?

2
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:25,890
I'll unleash my dog.

3
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:31,570
I'll unleash my dog!

4
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,200
Come on.

5
00:01:24,590 --> 00:01:25,120
All done?

6
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:41,550
An entire set of 9 pieces.

7
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,850
Not one missing.

8
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,259
Shut the doors.

9
00:03:28,100 --> 00:03:31,910
[Born with Luck]

10
00:03:31,930 --> 00:03:34,850
[Episode 15]

11
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:36,840
He is a bit shy.

12
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:40,010
-He is a bit shy.
-He is a bit shy.

13
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:40,800
Bit.

14
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:42,290
Bit.

15
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,030
Bit.

16
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:44,060
Bit.

17
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,710
Halt.

18
00:03:56,750 --> 00:03:57,680
Are you a parent?

19
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:01,210
Someone's sister?

20
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:09,540
You're here to learn English
as well, right?

21
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,380
I'm here to take a look.

22
00:04:15,470 --> 00:04:17,750
Too embarrassed to go to an institute
for adults

23
00:04:17,750 --> 00:04:19,610
and afraid of failing to catch up?

24
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,600
This place is great
for learning the basics.

25
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,000
You chose the right spot.

26
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,130
A-Are you listening

27
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:28,490
to English?

28
00:04:28,750 --> 00:04:29,830
Could you let me hear it?

29
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:31,430
We can share our experience.

30
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,650
Let me hear it.

31
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,190
It's out of battery.

32
00:04:34,190 --> 00:04:34,990
Take a listen.

33
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,130
What a pity.

34
00:04:41,430 --> 00:04:42,430
Nice to meet you.

35
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:43,470
I'm Peter.

36
00:04:47,070 --> 00:04:47,600
I'm Cici.

37
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:58,760
I took English classes with him
for 3 days.

38
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:00,310
Back in my school days,

39
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:02,070
I felt sleepy whenever I heard English.

40
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:04,160
The course lasted from 8 a.m. to 9 a.m.,

41
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,420
and then 8 p.m. to 9 p.m.

42
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:08,510
You're so lucky to watch Li Penggai,

43
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:10,310
since you don't need to leave home early

44
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,370
and come home late.

45
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:13,600
Do you know what kind of sacrifice

46
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,930
I made in the past 3 days?

47
00:05:15,540 --> 00:05:17,350
[Mapleleaf Peninsula]

48
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,160
I went undercover

49
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,720
at the sales centers
of various new-builds.

50
00:05:17,470 --> 00:05:21,850
[Mapleleaf Peninsula,
a 5A-level haven for the body and mind ]

51
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:22,950
Sir.

52
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,480
Sir, interested in the apartments?

53
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:26,630
How much per square meter?

54
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:28,090
How much per square meter?

55
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,560
-Fifteen thousand yuan.
-Thirty thousand yuan.

56
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,560
-Such a low price?
-That expensive?

57
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:33,680
Since when did you become so rich?

58
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,880
I don't have a budget.

59
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,310
I'll pay as much as it takes.

60
00:05:36,310 --> 00:05:37,280
He took snacks

61
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,200
and stole an umbrella

62
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:40,920
after seeing the new-builds.

63
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,650
Then, he went to have Malatang.

64
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:49,680
Bro!

65
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,330
We just met at the sales center.

66
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:55,190
I had Malatang with him for 3 days.

67
00:05:55,190 --> 00:05:55,680
This is delicious.

68
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,080
I got terrible diarrhea.

69
00:06:03,430 --> 00:06:04,630
Don't get us started.

70
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:07,300
We had to stake out till early morning
every day.

71
00:06:08,630 --> 00:06:10,070
Mr. Lang, slow down.

72
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:10,920
Careful.

73
00:06:10,590 --> 00:06:12,110
[Auto focus]

74
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:13,920
-Bye!
-Bye!

75
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:14,830
Bye!

76
00:06:23,990 --> 00:06:25,790
[Auto focus]

77
00:06:44,970 --> 00:06:46,500
Team 4 has taken over. Over.

78
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:52,630
Li Qian?

79
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:54,310
She's not on our team.

80
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:55,000
Maybe it's her shift

81
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,130
to watch Hu Jianren.

82
00:06:56,159 --> 00:06:57,020
Ask about that.

83
00:06:58,510 --> 00:07:00,310
Team 1, please respond to Team 4.

84
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,840
Team 1, please respond to Team 4.

85
00:07:08,030 --> 00:07:09,030
There are police.

86
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:14,990
Team 1, please respond to Team 4.

87
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:51,960
[Xinda Advertisement]

88
00:07:44,850 --> 00:07:46,380
What kind of driver are you?

89
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:01,650
How could you drive like that?

90
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:03,490
I'm really sorry.

91
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:05,510
C-C-Call the police.

92
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,220
Team 2, get back into your car.

93
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:13,430
Do not blow your cover at this point.

94
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,600
Observe first.

95
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,830
The driver of the runaway car
takes full responsibility.

96
00:08:26,830 --> 00:08:27,630
Any problem with that?

97
00:08:27,630 --> 00:08:28,190
No.

98
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,800
Your IDs and driver's licenses.

99
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:36,720
Is this car yours?

100
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,200
No.

101
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,720
It belongs to Rongcheng Group.

102
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,780
It's my boss's car.

103
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,840
What's your boss's name?

104
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:44,720
Zhou Rong,

105
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:46,160
Mr. Zhou.

106
00:08:47,530 --> 00:08:48,260
[Traffic Police Unit of Sanjiangkou
Public Security Bureau, Ping'an Province]

107
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,030
[Traffic Accident Ruling]

108
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:50,390
And yours?

109
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:52,050
I forgot to bring mine.

110
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:54,790
Do you or do you not have
a driver's license?

111
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:01,770
Your ID number?

112
00:09:01,870 --> 00:09:02,550
Ren.

113
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,690
Ren.

114
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:05,010
What happened?

115
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:06,090
Nothing.

116
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,870
Just a little fender bender.

117
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:09,080
The responsibility is all hers.

118
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:09,670
Cici?

119
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:12,560
Mr. Zhou,

120
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,580
I've met this girl before.

121
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:16,480
An acquaintance of yours?

122
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,440
Not really.

123
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,570
How did you meet her?

124
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,720
Just by chance.

125
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,840
Make sure you drive carefully
in the future.

126
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,370
Mr. Zhou,

127
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,750
this has nothing to do with us.

128
00:09:28,750 --> 00:09:29,390
She rear-ended our car.

129
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:30,000
Gorgeous.

130
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,530
Did you get hurt?

131
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:32,660
No.

132
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,840
That's good.

133
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:34,960
The car is mine.

134
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,350
We'll pay for the repair.

135
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:38,150
How are you involved in this now?

136
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,720
You think that's a proper parking place?

137
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,720
Move your car now!

138
00:09:43,510 --> 00:09:44,970
Don't give her a hard time.

139
00:09:47,380 --> 00:09:48,580
Here, sign your name.

140
00:09:58,750 --> 00:10:00,200
Does she have a driver's license?

141
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,530
Mind your own business.

142
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,240
[Zhang Yi'ang]

143
00:10:12,940 --> 00:10:14,540
Come back to the station now.

144
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,240
One copy for each of you.

145
00:10:23,790 --> 00:10:24,200
What's up

146
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,670
with your luck today?

147
00:10:25,690 --> 00:10:26,220
Oh you...

148
00:10:26,550 --> 00:10:28,080
You crashed the car so soon.

149
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:28,870
To add to it, Mr. Zhou

150
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:30,080
and Ren s-saw everything.

151
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:30,480
Bro,

152
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,310
I am really not to blame.

153
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,510
The car ahead changed lanes
over a solid line.

154
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:35,720
The one behind rear-ended mine.

155
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,120
None of that was my fault.

156
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:40,850
Does Ren want me to pay for the repair?

157
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,440
Don't talk nonsense.

158
00:10:42,910 --> 00:10:44,310
Ren is not that petty.

159
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,240
Alright. T-The...

160
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,750
The responsibility is really not yours.

161
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:48,840
Look, just claim the repair

162
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,900
on insurance.

163
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:51,960
Alright. Don't be mad.

164
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,560
Calm down.

165
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:54,020
How can I not be mad?

166
00:10:58,030 --> 00:11:00,200
The thing is, the car ahead ran away.

167
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:01,960
All the company cars only

168
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,960
have mandatory liability insurance
for traffic accidents.

169
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:06,360
The company has to pay
for any repair first.

170
00:11:06,550 --> 00:11:07,640
How am I supposed

171
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,780
to talk about that with Ren?

172
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:10,240
No.

173
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,260
Just be frank with him.

174
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:14,270
That car ran away.
What's there for us to do?

175
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:14,730
Well...

176
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,030
When the offending driver is caught,

177
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:17,270
w-we'll be able to pay the company back,

178
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:17,960
right?

179
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,320
Should I also be frank with Mr. Zhou

180
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,910
when he asks why I used the car?

181
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:22,270
Am I going to tell him
that I let my girlfriend

182
00:11:22,270 --> 00:11:23,630
borrow it
for the wedding vendor she works for?

183
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:24,540
Of course not.

184
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,920
Are you silly or what?

185
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:31,310
Gai,

186
00:11:32,650 --> 00:11:33,270
you're much

187
00:11:33,270 --> 00:11:34,600
favored by Mr. Zhou now.

188
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:35,360
You...

189
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,250
You're supposed to be

190
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,210
at the same level as Ren.

191
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:42,490
How about you put in a good word
for me with Ren?

192
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:45,670
Wait.

193
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:49,020
Is it so obvious
that I'm favored by Mr. Zhou now?

194
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:51,630
Yes, very much so.

195
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:54,610
Everyone in the company can see that.

196
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,970
Gai, think about it.

197
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,600
Mr. Zhou has a bad temper.

198
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,200
Many of his subordinates

199
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:01,000
have been sent to transport sand.

200
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,360
Has any of them come back?

201
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:02,720
Right.

202
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,920
You're an exception.

203
00:12:04,150 --> 00:12:05,390
You're the one and only exception.

204
00:12:05,390 --> 00:12:06,390
Alright, stop it.

205
00:12:06,450 --> 00:12:07,870
If you're not favored by him,

206
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:08,780
then who is?

207
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:11,600
Well, I...

208
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,120
Ren is here.

209
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:16,070
Gai,

210
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,440
you must help me.

211
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,870
This matter involves you too.

212
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:21,200
It was you who allowed me
to borrow the car.

213
00:12:21,890 --> 00:12:22,440
Fine.

214
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:24,520
I'll fix the problem for you.

215
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:30,600
Ren,

216
00:12:31,630 --> 00:12:32,520
well...

217
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,550
Cong had a little crash

218
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:36,920
when he used the car.

219
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:39,700
I'll have it fixed
in a friend's repair shop.

220
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,260
Ren...

221
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:52,510
Do you know why I slapped you?

222
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:53,920
Didn't I tell you

223
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:55,230
to behave these days?

224
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:57,210
But you messed with the police.

225
00:12:58,030 --> 00:12:59,490
It was the traffic police.

226
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:02,790
Gai...

227
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,920
Not even the traffic police!

228
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:06,960
What's wrong with you for lending

229
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,510
a company car to your girlfriend?

230
00:13:08,510 --> 00:13:09,720
You will pay

231
00:13:10,390 --> 00:13:11,590
for the car repair.

232
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:21,720
How much?

233
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,170
But isn't it just

234
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:26,600
fixing the dented front bumper?

235
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:29,020
How could it cost 30,000 yuan?

236
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:30,800
Bro,

237
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:32,080
this is Mr. Zhou's car.

238
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,430
Mr. Zhou Rong's car.

239
00:13:33,630 --> 00:13:34,760
Let's negotiate it.

240
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,150
Yes. Calculate it again.

241
00:13:39,150 --> 00:13:39,510
No.

242
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:42,090
Why are you still charging for 30,000?

243
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:42,910
Hello?

244
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:45,000
Hello?

245
00:13:54,290 --> 00:13:54,520
[Traffic Accident Ruling]

246
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:55,110
[Specifics of the accident]

247
00:13:55,130 --> 00:13:56,910
[Signatures of the parties involved:
Du Cong, Li Qian]

248
00:14:01,030 --> 00:14:01,480
Hello.

249
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:02,560
Hello?

250
00:14:03,270 --> 00:14:04,080
Is it Ms. Li?

251
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:07,200
I was driving the car
that you just rear-ended.

252
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:07,860
I'm Du Cong.

253
00:14:09,200 --> 00:14:10,260
What's the matter?

254
00:14:11,510 --> 00:14:14,400
Do you know how traffic accidents

255
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,180
are processed?

256
00:14:17,290 --> 00:14:18,360
No.

257
00:14:18,870 --> 00:14:20,400
Just tell me why you called.

258
00:14:22,910 --> 00:14:24,370
I'd like to claim damages.

259
00:14:24,390 --> 00:14:25,290
Claim damages?

260
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:27,080
Shouldn't you talk
to the insurance company?

261
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,200
Here's the thing.

262
00:14:28,870 --> 00:14:30,120
That car ahead of me

263
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,680
ran away, didn't it?

264
00:14:32,110 --> 00:14:34,550
At that time, you didn't have your ID on.

265
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,460
According to

266
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:37,840
the Road Traffic Safety Law

267
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:39,770
of the People's Republic of China,

268
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:42,080
you need to pay for damaging

269
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,540
the front bumper of my car.

270
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,870
It's 30,000 yuan in total.

271
00:14:44,870 --> 00:14:47,000
How would you like to make the payment?

272
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:49,390
Hello?

273
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:54,240
Hey, Ms. Li.

274
00:14:54,510 --> 00:14:56,770
You can't solve a problem by avoiding it.

275
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:59,000
I-It's all clearly stated in the law.

276
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,720
The traffic police has records
about the incident.

277
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,530
I don’t have that much money.

278
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:03,840
Mr. Du,

279
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:06,480
is there any other solution?

280
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,480
There is indeed

281
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:12,960
a solution.

282
00:15:15,010 --> 00:15:16,470
Don't give her a hard time.

283
00:15:21,150 --> 00:15:22,000
Plus, I think

284
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,550
it could be a good opportunity

285
00:15:23,550 --> 00:15:24,690
for you.

286
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:27,390
I work for Rongcheng Group.

287
00:15:27,550 --> 00:15:29,610
You're aware that you damaged

288
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:31,320
Mr. Zhou Rong's car, right?

289
00:15:31,630 --> 00:15:32,390
Yes, I know.

290
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,030
Mr. Zhou

291
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:35,830
is single.

292
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:39,280
I can arrange a meeting for you

293
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:40,130
and Mr. Zhou,

294
00:15:40,550 --> 00:15:42,240
in which you can own up to your mistake.

295
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:43,790
If you manage to please

296
00:15:43,790 --> 00:15:44,630
Mr. Zhou,

297
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:45,780
young lady,

298
00:15:46,630 --> 00:15:48,750
you won't need to pay for the car repair,
will you?

299
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:49,840
The rest of your life

300
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:50,870
will be secured.

301
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,670
This is a great opportunity.

302
00:15:52,670 --> 00:15:53,820
I wouldn't even offer it

303
00:15:53,820 --> 00:15:54,790
to my own sister.

304
00:15:54,790 --> 00:15:55,750
But I'm offering it to you now.

305
00:15:55,750 --> 00:15:56,910
Aren't I kind to you?

306
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:58,680
What do you say?

307
00:15:59,150 --> 00:16:00,800
Thank you so much.

308
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,630
When the meeting is scheduled,

309
00:16:02,630 --> 00:16:03,720
call me anytime.

310
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:05,600
Okay.

311
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:13,690
Mr. Guo,

312
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:15,030
are you really urging me to pay

313
00:16:15,030 --> 00:16:17,290
that mere construction fee of 7 million?

314
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:19,280
I'm a man of my word.

315
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:21,360
I'll transfer it to you in a few days.

316
00:16:25,500 --> 00:16:26,140
Well...

317
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,350
Mr. Zhou,

318
00:16:27,790 --> 00:16:28,410
our money

319
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,910
is saved for buying bianzhong.

320
00:16:29,910 --> 00:16:31,110
What should we do now?

321
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:32,570
Do you know why geese

322
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:33,910
fly south in winter?

323
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:34,860
Yes, I know.

324
00:16:35,030 --> 00:16:37,090
Because walking takes too much time.

325
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:39,360
No, it's because it is too cold
in the north
when winter comes.

326
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:41,490
Planning ahead is a must. Understood?

327
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:43,910
Half of the money has been transferred to

328
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:45,360
to the Republic of St. Marlino.

329
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:47,820
The other half has been transferred
to Tuva.

330
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:50,480
It'll travel around the south hemisphere.

331
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:52,540
By the time the money gets to Okabana,

332
00:16:52,630 --> 00:16:53,320
we'll be watching

333
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:55,410
the sunset at a beach in Africa.

334
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:58,450
Nothing has happened lately, has it?

335
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:01,770
Just one small thing.

336
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:04,810
Du Cong hopes to apologize to you
for it in person.

337
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:05,720
That's unnecessary.

338
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:06,270
Mr. Zhou.

339
00:17:11,109 --> 00:17:12,310
Mr. Zhou, I did wrong.

340
00:17:12,589 --> 00:17:15,520
I shouldn't have used a company car
without consent.

341
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:20,510
Mr. Zhou.

342
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:22,660
Mr. Zhou...

343
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:23,319
Cut it out.

344
00:17:24,339 --> 00:17:25,089
Listen,

345
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:26,880
Mr. Zhou has been busy

346
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:27,940
and grumpy lately.

347
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:29,480
I happen to have some good news

348
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,550
for Mr. Zhou.

349
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:33,110
Perhaps it'll help him
blow off some steam.

350
00:17:33,110 --> 00:17:34,040
It's a surprise.

351
00:17:34,070 --> 00:17:34,790
No way.

352
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:36,630
Surprise me first.

353
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:37,680
What's the news?

354
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:40,480
Do you remember the girl

355
00:17:41,070 --> 00:17:42,110
who rear-ended our car?

356
00:17:42,110 --> 00:17:43,040
What's with her?

357
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:45,730
She seems to have a crush

358
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,110
on Mr. Zhou.

359
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:50,010
So, she asked if I could arrange a meeting

360
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:51,370
for her and Mr. Zhou.

361
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:52,650
I'd like to know

362
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:54,410
if Mr. Zhou is interested in it.

363
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:56,350
Mr. Zhou did take a few glances at her.

364
00:17:56,350 --> 00:17:57,950
Those were not just glances.

365
00:17:58,070 --> 00:18:00,270
He couldn't take his eyes off her at all.

366
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,850
I've got it all settled with that girl.

367
00:18:03,110 --> 00:18:03,700
Okay.

368
00:18:03,790 --> 00:18:04,550
You did a good job in this.

369
00:18:04,550 --> 00:18:06,410
I'll tell Mr. Zhou the news later.

370
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,000
Does that girl

371
00:18:09,310 --> 00:18:10,370
eat chives?

372
00:18:13,040 --> 00:18:14,210
How would I know?

373
00:18:15,070 --> 00:18:16,800
Just tell her not to eat chives.

374
00:18:17,030 --> 00:18:17,480
Ren.

375
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:18,240
What now?

376
00:18:19,110 --> 00:18:20,240
Do I still have to...

377
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:21,980
pay for the car repair?

378
00:18:22,550 --> 00:18:23,410
Yes, of course.

379
00:18:23,750 --> 00:18:25,880
Are you asking me
to pay for your mistake instead?

380
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:26,720
You're out of your mind.

381
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:27,320
Go away!

382
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:28,960
How annoying.

383
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,510
Do not let this man in again.

384
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:34,860
How are you?

385
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:38,410
I...

386
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:39,270
A-Any injuries anywhere?

387
00:18:39,270 --> 00:18:39,680
Just tell me

388
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:40,480
where you're injured.

389
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,600
I'm not injured.

390
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:43,860
It was just a rear-end collision.

391
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,160
But the car I rear-ended

392
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:46,760
belongs to Rongcheng Group.

393
00:18:46,790 --> 00:18:47,200
I know.

394
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:49,720
Did you tell that driver you're a cop?

395
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:50,240
No.

396
00:18:51,310 --> 00:18:52,960
It happened when I was on the way

397
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:53,880
to meet Team 3.

398
00:18:58,650 --> 00:19:00,510
It was really a traffic accident.

399
00:19:03,740 --> 00:19:04,450
It's true!

400
00:19:07,030 --> 00:19:08,790
A situation has come up.

401
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:11,570
Today, 3 cars rear-ended each other.

402
00:19:11,590 --> 00:19:13,590
The driver of the car ahead has fled.

403
00:19:13,790 --> 00:19:15,110
Just now, the driver of the car
in the middle,

404
00:19:15,110 --> 00:19:16,680
who works for Rongcheng Group,

405
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:18,240
called and asked me for compensation.

406
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:19,370
I said I had no money.

407
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:21,030
Then he said he could arrange

408
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:22,690
a meeting for me and Zhou Rong,

409
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:24,830
after which I won't have to
pay for the damage.

410
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:25,720
A meeting?

411
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:28,210
Yes, a meeting.

412
00:19:29,750 --> 00:19:30,810
How did you answer?

413
00:19:34,110 --> 00:19:35,370
I-I thought it was

414
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:36,240
a good opportunity

415
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:37,090
to approach Zhou Rong.

416
00:19:37,090 --> 00:19:37,750
So, I said yes.

417
00:19:37,750 --> 00:19:38,690
You thought?

418
00:19:38,790 --> 00:19:39,550
Didn't we tell you

419
00:19:39,550 --> 00:19:41,510
the undercover plan wouldn't work?

420
00:19:41,510 --> 00:19:43,160
Why did you take action
without consent again?

421
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,640
I didn't take action without consent.

422
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:45,830
One thing led to another.

423
00:19:45,830 --> 00:19:46,960
I just had to say yes.

424
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:47,890
If you disagree with it,

425
00:19:47,890 --> 00:19:48,550
I won't go meet him.

426
00:19:48,550 --> 00:19:49,240
Why are we back

427
00:19:49,240 --> 00:19:50,500
to the undercover plan again?

428
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:51,160
Didn't we tell you

429
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:51,880
that it'd at least

430
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:53,510
take you 3 to 5 years to gain their trust?

431
00:19:53,510 --> 00:19:55,240
Chief Zhang opposed it for your own good.

432
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:56,030
He's worried about you.

433
00:19:56,030 --> 00:19:56,920
I know.

434
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:02,100
Alright. Y-You go do your job.

435
00:20:04,310 --> 00:20:05,840
I won't meet with Zhou Rong.

436
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:14,640
What an upstanding girl, for knowing

437
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:15,400
that she can't cross the line.

438
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:16,260
Stop talking.

439
00:20:16,510 --> 00:20:17,370
Unfathomable.

440
00:20:29,330 --> 00:20:31,060
You're disheartened already?

441
00:20:35,090 --> 00:20:36,470
You're so lame.

442
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:38,640
You still don't know me well.

443
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:41,200
I always have my friends' backs.

444
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:44,180
How can I not help you
when you're in trouble?

445
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:45,900
I've informed

446
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:46,680
my friends

447
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:48,080
working in repair shops.

448
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:49,640
Once this coward sends his car

449
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:51,070
for repair, I'll know it right away.

450
00:20:51,070 --> 00:20:53,400
Then we can get
the repair fee back, right?

451
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:56,680
Really?

452
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:01,070
We'll even extort him and make him

453
00:21:01,070 --> 00:21:02,470
pay more than repair fee.

454
00:21:02,750 --> 00:21:03,960
H-He will have to compensate you.

455
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:04,810
Yes, extort him.

456
00:21:04,810 --> 00:21:06,410
Let's demand compensation.

457
00:21:08,510 --> 00:21:09,840
I was thinking about...

458
00:21:10,640 --> 00:21:11,270
What?

459
00:21:11,980 --> 00:21:12,980
It's of no use now.

460
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:15,670
Gai,

461
00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:21,530
I made a right decision of following you.

462
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:24,510
Cong.

463
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:26,400
You see,

464
00:21:27,840 --> 00:21:29,900
sometimes, money can buy obedience,

465
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:31,640
but not loyalty.

466
00:21:32,030 --> 00:21:33,630
As long as you are loyal to me,

467
00:21:34,590 --> 00:21:36,190
you'll have a bright future.

468
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,530
Bro,

469
00:21:52,550 --> 00:21:53,880
I am really starving.

470
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:57,060
There's only one blade of grass left.

471
00:21:57,750 --> 00:22:00,350
The leaves are for you,
and I'll take the stalk.

472
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:04,160
What then?

473
00:22:04,880 --> 00:22:06,280
Shall we just wait to die?

474
00:22:07,830 --> 00:22:09,890
Why the topic of death all of a sudden?

475
00:22:11,750 --> 00:22:13,210
When someone passes here,

476
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:14,750
we'll be saved, right?

477
00:22:16,270 --> 00:22:17,240
It's been 3 days.

478
00:22:18,830 --> 00:22:20,350
Has anyone passed by?

479
00:22:30,830 --> 00:22:31,960
Someone's up there.

480
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:44,110
Wait, bro,

481
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:46,170
he can help us out, right?

482
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:47,920
Who else other than those from the court

483
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:48,850
would come here?

484
00:22:51,580 --> 00:22:52,770
Even if they help us out,

485
00:22:52,770 --> 00:22:53,870
will they let us go?

486
00:23:52,310 --> 00:23:52,960
What for?

487
00:23:53,070 --> 00:23:54,130
Grocery delivery.

488
00:23:54,680 --> 00:23:55,740
Grocery delivery?

489
00:24:04,050 --> 00:24:05,520
You didn't use to serve us, did you?

490
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:06,920
No, we didn't. We're newly hired.

491
00:24:06,920 --> 00:24:08,510
Our company is getting started.

492
00:24:08,510 --> 00:24:09,400
So the prices are low.

493
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:10,580
Yes, low prices.

494
00:24:12,270 --> 00:24:13,130
Open the trunk.

495
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:14,040
-Sure.
-Sure.

496
00:24:14,070 --> 00:24:14,600
Show him.

497
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:15,070
Yes.

498
00:24:19,240 --> 00:24:20,830
[Baoku Fresh Produce Delivery Center]

499
00:24:25,480 --> 00:24:26,010
Alright.

500
00:24:26,310 --> 00:24:27,310
Drive the truck in.

501
00:24:27,310 --> 00:24:27,640
Okay.

502
00:24:30,070 --> 00:24:30,500
Okay.

503
00:24:30,520 --> 00:24:31,320
Open the gate.

504
00:24:40,540 --> 00:24:41,270
Uncle Yifei,

505
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:43,200
no problem. Our plan is working.

506
00:24:41,890 --> 00:24:45,800
[Baoku Fresh Produce]

507
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,360
We can proceed anytime.

508
00:24:54,030 --> 00:24:54,750
Mr. Zhou,

509
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:55,920
Zhu Yifei called and scheduled

510
00:24:55,920 --> 00:24:57,510
the transaction for tomorrow.

511
00:24:57,510 --> 00:24:58,200
Tomorrow?

512
00:24:59,790 --> 00:25:01,070
Didn't we agree to postpone it?

513
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:02,670
Why did he move it up instead?

514
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:03,480
Do people in this line

515
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:04,750
of business just act at will?

516
00:25:04,750 --> 00:25:05,880
He'll do as we asked.

517
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:07,240
Tomorrow, he'll bring the bianzhong over

518
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:08,070
for us to check.

519
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:09,310
If there's no problem,

520
00:25:09,310 --> 00:25:10,830
we'll make the transaction.

521
00:25:10,830 --> 00:25:12,090
Is the money prepared?

522
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:14,270
Contact Fang Yong then.

523
00:25:14,270 --> 00:25:15,110
Have him examine the items himself.

524
00:25:15,110 --> 00:25:15,510
Got it.

525
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:18,070
As long as we land on
the East New Town project,

526
00:25:18,070 --> 00:25:18,750
all the problems

527
00:25:18,750 --> 00:25:19,910
will be solved.

528
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:21,820
Mr. Zhou,

529
00:25:23,350 --> 00:25:25,480
you've worked really hard these days.

530
00:25:29,590 --> 00:25:30,840
Li Penggai is here.

531
00:25:31,270 --> 00:25:32,730
Would you like to meet him?

532
00:25:33,680 --> 00:25:35,350
He's been through a lot as well,

533
00:25:35,350 --> 00:25:37,590
for eating dust
at the construction site for days.

534
00:25:37,590 --> 00:25:38,720
He must feel bitter.

535
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:40,450
I'm sure he needs your comfort.

536
00:25:40,750 --> 00:25:42,280
Is it what a boss needs to do?

537
00:25:43,030 --> 00:25:44,230
But if I do it instead,

538
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:46,340
he won't feel your care for him.

539
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:48,550
Let him in.

540
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:51,480
Li Penggai, come in!

541
00:25:57,880 --> 00:25:58,700
Mr. Zhou!

542
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:00,000
D-Don't kneel.

543
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,330
G-Give him 10,000 yuan.

544
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:03,580
No, 20,000.

545
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:04,290
Get up.

546
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:05,010
Mr. Zhou,

547
00:26:05,350 --> 00:26:06,410
I don't want money.

548
00:26:07,510 --> 00:26:08,510
I hope to stay around you.

549
00:26:08,510 --> 00:26:09,510
I'm done working on the construction site.

550
00:26:09,510 --> 00:26:10,610
I understand why you make me go there,

551
00:26:10,610 --> 00:26:12,240
but I still want to stay with you
and serve you.

552
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,200
Why must you stick with me?

553
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:14,180
This is a reward

554
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:15,300
for your hard work.

555
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:17,510
Mr. Zhou, I really don't want any money.

556
00:26:17,510 --> 00:26:19,310
All I want is to stay by your side.

557
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:21,000
I know...

558
00:26:22,350 --> 00:26:23,480
among all the people around you,

559
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:24,680
Ren is only loyal one.

560
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:26,080
I want to be a second one.

561
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:27,640
As you said, Mr. Zhou,

562
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:29,150
money can buy obedience,

563
00:26:29,550 --> 00:26:30,590
but not loyalty.

564
00:26:32,150 --> 00:26:33,680
It sounds quite familiar.

565
00:26:41,160 --> 00:26:42,560
When did you

566
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:44,420
hear me say that?

567
00:26:45,680 --> 00:26:46,540
Half a year ago,

568
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:49,140
that rainy and windy night

569
00:26:50,350 --> 00:26:51,950
left a deep impression on me.

570
00:26:54,790 --> 00:26:55,790
Move it a bit more.

571
00:26:56,070 --> 00:26:56,590
Stop!

572
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,640
Let me take a look.

573
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,310
All of you, get out.

574
00:27:02,310 --> 00:27:03,030
It's almost done, Mr. Zhou.

575
00:27:03,030 --> 00:27:03,520
Get out!

576
00:27:05,070 --> 00:27:05,880
Now!

577
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:17,200
Where is my phone?

578
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:22,020
Did I leave it in the study?

579
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:39,510
W-Will I be scolded

580
00:27:39,510 --> 00:27:40,640
if I get in there now?

581
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:41,750
Dial my number.

582
00:27:41,750 --> 00:27:42,610
Do it yourself.

583
00:27:50,510 --> 00:27:51,000
Bowen.

584
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:02,320
Money can buy obedience,

585
00:28:02,340 --> 00:28:03,590
but not loyalty.

586
00:28:04,890 --> 00:28:06,020
Among all the people

587
00:28:06,350 --> 00:28:07,550
around me now, you are

588
00:28:07,890 --> 00:28:08,950
the only loyal one.

589
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:21,210
Mr. Zhou knows

590
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:23,050
what's on your mind.

591
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:23,720
Here.

592
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:25,070
Take the money.

593
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,200
Is it appropriate?

594
00:28:26,200 --> 00:28:26,640
Scram.

595
00:28:26,830 --> 00:28:27,310
Fine.

596
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:36,110
Why did he bring up

597
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:37,440
what happened that day?

598
00:28:48,310 --> 00:28:49,070
All of you, get out.

599
00:28:49,070 --> 00:28:50,110
It's almost done, Mr. Zhou.

600
00:28:50,110 --> 00:28:50,850
Get out!

601
00:28:51,850 --> 00:28:52,610
Let's go.

602
00:28:53,720 --> 00:28:54,480
Now!

603
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:01,350
Bowen.

604
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:24,830
How very nice.

605
00:29:35,270 --> 00:29:35,800
Mr. Zhou,

606
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:37,740
I finished the task

607
00:29:37,830 --> 00:29:39,000
without anyone knowing.

608
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:39,930
It was flawless.

609
00:29:40,200 --> 00:29:41,640
Why did you have to kill him?

610
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:42,880
He was chief
of the Public Security Bureau.

611
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:43,510
Deputy chief.

612
00:29:43,510 --> 00:29:44,510
That is no excuse!

613
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:47,830
Lu Zheng stood in your way

614
00:29:47,830 --> 00:29:48,830
several times,

615
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:50,160
and picked on Ye Jian.

616
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,550
You said that you wanted him dead,

617
00:29:51,550 --> 00:29:53,200
so that everyone would know
who's in charge of Sanjiangkou.

618
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:56,130
I was just saying it.
How could it be taken seriously?

619
00:29:56,310 --> 00:29:58,240
Find something to smash the phone!

620
00:29:59,000 --> 00:29:59,570
Mr. Zhou,

621
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:01,270
I took the risk of killing him

622
00:30:01,270 --> 00:30:03,200
-on your order.
-What was my order?

623
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:05,480
I already killed Lu Zheng.

624
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:07,540
You have to keep your promise, right?

625
00:30:07,720 --> 00:30:09,050
Come here. Give it to me!

626
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:10,950
Give it to me.

627
00:30:12,270 --> 00:30:12,930
Mr. Zhou...

628
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:26,480
Burn it.

629
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:45,280
Mr. Zhou,

630
00:30:46,030 --> 00:30:47,310
Lu Zheng's death is good news

631
00:30:47,310 --> 00:30:48,130
to us.

632
00:30:48,830 --> 00:30:50,270
From now on, in Sanjiangkou,

633
00:30:50,270 --> 00:30:51,790
nobody will dare stand in your way.

634
00:30:51,790 --> 00:30:52,440
Bowen,

635
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:55,210
I’ll give you what you deserve.

636
00:30:55,350 --> 00:30:56,640
Just keep this matter secret,

637
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:57,120
okay?

638
00:30:57,680 --> 00:30:58,410
Don't worry.

639
00:30:58,830 --> 00:31:00,830
It's all been burned into ashes now.

640
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:02,880
Thanks, Mr. Zhou.

641
00:31:12,030 --> 00:31:12,590
Mr. Zhou,

642
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:15,520
what is done can't be undone.

643
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,290
Don't overthink it.

644
00:31:28,270 --> 00:31:29,670
Money can buy obedience,

645
00:31:31,270 --> 00:31:32,200
but not loyalty.

646
00:31:34,270 --> 00:31:35,670
Now, among all the people

647
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:37,480
around me, you are

648
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:40,940
the only loyal one.

649
00:31:51,270 --> 00:31:53,030
He heard what I said to you.

650
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:55,550
Did he also hear what Lang Bowen

651
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:57,230
did to Lu Zheng?

652
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:58,110
Li Penggai definitely

653
00:31:58,110 --> 00:31:59,370
doesn't know about it.

654
00:32:00,290 --> 00:32:01,960
I have a bad feeling about this.

655
00:32:01,960 --> 00:32:03,420
He doesn't know, Mr. Zhou.

656
00:32:06,030 --> 00:32:07,070
Just be wary of him.

657
00:32:07,070 --> 00:32:07,480
Got it.

658
00:32:08,350 --> 00:32:09,280
Go get prepared.

659
00:32:09,550 --> 00:32:11,680
No mistake is allowed
for tomorrow's transaction.

660
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:12,410
Understood.

661
00:32:26,310 --> 00:32:27,350
Hu Jianren works

662
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:29,070
in the office during the day,

663
00:32:29,070 --> 00:32:31,240
and attends English classes after work.

664
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,470
He speaks English when he

665
00:32:32,470 --> 00:32:33,720
orders food and puts gas in his car.

666
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:35,830
He even listens to English
in the bathroom.

667
00:32:35,830 --> 00:32:38,030
There's nothing suspicious about him.

668
00:32:38,070 --> 00:32:39,240
As for Li Penggai,

669
00:32:39,750 --> 00:32:41,200
he has been to all the new-builds

670
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:42,860
and 4S stores in Sanjiangkou.

671
00:32:43,790 --> 00:32:46,590
The most suspicious of all
is that Malatang place.

672
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:47,690
Chief Zhang,

673
00:32:48,030 --> 00:32:50,480
I got food poisoning.
Does it count as work injury?

674
00:32:50,480 --> 00:32:51,610
What about you guys?

675
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,440
Any findings?

676
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:56,930
Chief Zhang, Captain Wang,

677
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:59,200
we can't go on like this forever.

678
00:33:00,110 --> 00:33:01,710
So chatty today, aren't you?

679
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:02,880
Don't you think Chief Zhang

680
00:33:02,880 --> 00:33:04,880
also knows we can't do this forever?

681
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:06,510
But what other solutions are there

682
00:33:06,510 --> 00:33:08,310
except for what we're doing now?

683
00:33:13,110 --> 00:33:13,710
Everyone,

684
00:33:15,350 --> 00:33:17,480
you've worked really hard these days.

685
00:33:17,510 --> 00:33:19,030
But our efforts

686
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:20,540
didn't go to waste.

687
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:21,920
They've paid off.

688
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:25,770
Have you ever thought about

689
00:33:27,110 --> 00:33:28,720
why Zhou Rong's gang

690
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:29,890
has been so quiet

691
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:31,820
in recent days?

692
00:33:37,270 --> 00:33:39,470
Silence often falls before a great war.

693
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:42,900
I believe they will

694
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:44,610
make a big move tomorrow.

695
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:47,200
Why does it have to be tomorrow?

696
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,200
Why can't it be...

697
00:33:50,830 --> 00:33:51,960
It must be tomorrow.

698
00:33:53,400 --> 00:33:55,140
I just reported to Chief Zhang

699
00:33:55,790 --> 00:33:57,030
that Hu Jianren asked for leave

700
00:33:57,030 --> 00:33:58,890
from his English class tomorrow.

701
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:04,700
As the saying goes,

702
00:34:06,270 --> 00:34:08,000
"Feign when the enemy is weary;

703
00:34:08,670 --> 00:34:10,330
wait when the enemy is hungry;

704
00:34:10,630 --> 00:34:12,070
strike when the enemy is at ease."

705
00:34:12,070 --> 00:34:13,670
This is what we're thinking.

706
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:16,050
I bet Zhou Rong and his fellows also think

707
00:34:16,050 --> 00:34:17,650
this is what we're thinking.

708
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:20,219
So, they'll surely make a move tomorrow.

709
00:34:20,630 --> 00:34:22,030
We need to send them a message

710
00:34:22,030 --> 00:34:22,800
through action

711
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:23,670
that their guess

712
00:34:23,670 --> 00:34:25,330
about our guess is incorrect.

713
00:34:25,630 --> 00:34:27,290
The final battle is tomorrow.

714
00:34:28,630 --> 00:34:29,070
Okay.

715
00:34:35,590 --> 00:34:36,630
Li Qian, you don't need to take part

716
00:34:36,630 --> 00:34:38,090
in tomorrow's operation.

717
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,000
Why?

718
00:34:40,030 --> 00:34:41,000
A more important task

719
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:41,659
awaits you.

720
00:34:46,070 --> 00:34:46,670
Eat up.

721
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:54,520
Mr. Zhou needs a car tomorrow

722
00:34:54,550 --> 00:34:55,590
to pick up a big shot.

723
00:34:55,590 --> 00:34:56,880
Is that S600 model fixed?

724
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:57,720
Yes, Bowen.

725
00:34:58,110 --> 00:35:00,510
Who's the big shot?
I'll pick him up myself.

726
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:02,740
Let someone else do it.

727
00:35:03,070 --> 00:35:04,280
Mr. Zhou has an important task

728
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:04,920
for you.

729
00:35:07,030 --> 00:35:07,710
Okay.

730
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:09,330
T-Then let's send Du Cong to it.

731
00:35:09,330 --> 00:35:10,070
Though he often takes

732
00:35:10,070 --> 00:35:11,000
advantage of everything,

733
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:13,510
he's the most reliable
among all our fellows.

734
00:35:13,510 --> 00:35:14,570
You handle it then.

735
00:35:24,150 --> 00:35:25,230
Why did you pull up the car here?

736
00:35:25,230 --> 00:35:26,360
It's blocking the way.

737
00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:28,160
I left you some space there, see?

738
00:35:58,230 --> 00:35:58,880
Are you...

739
00:35:59,190 --> 00:36:00,060
Mr. Fang?

740
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:07,420
Why such an eye-catching car?

741
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:08,230
Picking up a big shot like you

742
00:36:08,230 --> 00:36:09,830
calls for a presentable car.

743
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:10,630
Hurry and leave.

744
00:36:10,630 --> 00:36:11,150
Get a move on.

745
00:36:11,150 --> 00:36:13,680
I pulled up the car here
for your convenience.

746
00:36:30,630 --> 00:36:32,110
How many savory crispy crepes?

747
00:36:32,110 --> 00:36:32,530
Two.

748
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:33,030
Got it.

749
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:35,280
Here you are.

750
00:36:35,710 --> 00:36:36,210
Thanks.

751
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:37,710
Alright. Take care.
Don't forget your soy milk.

752
00:36:37,710 --> 00:36:38,440
Here you are.

753
00:36:39,670 --> 00:36:40,520
Okay, bye.

754
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:44,110
I thought it was an important task.

755
00:36:44,110 --> 00:36:46,770
As it turns out,
I'm only assigned to fix the car.

756
00:36:48,990 --> 00:36:50,560
[No riding, dancing, singing, or gathering
in the parking lot]

757
00:36:50,580 --> 00:36:51,510
[Any consequences will be on you]

758
00:37:00,710 --> 00:37:03,010
[No riding, dancing, singing, or gathering
in the parking lot]

759
00:37:03,030 --> 00:37:05,260
[Any consequences will be on you]

760
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:06,930
I have to hang up now.

761
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:20,880
Place the 8 large ones in this truck.

762
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:21,840
Be gentle.

763
00:37:29,070 --> 00:37:31,000
Have Liu Bei carry the small one.

764
00:37:31,070 --> 00:37:32,230
[Baoku Fresh Produce]

765
00:37:31,110 --> 00:37:31,770
Be careful.

766
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:32,150
Here.

767
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:36,650
Boss, here you are.

768
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:38,170
Five.

769
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:39,110
Here, six.

770
00:37:39,960 --> 00:37:40,590
Seven.

771
00:38:10,070 --> 00:38:10,620
Come on.

772
00:38:10,840 --> 00:38:12,170
Is all the stuff loaded?

773
00:38:12,630 --> 00:38:13,740
Shut the rear door.

774
00:38:15,610 --> 00:38:16,540
Close that door.

775
00:38:26,400 --> 00:38:28,260
After I enter that place,

776
00:38:28,630 --> 00:38:29,630
I'll call you.

777
00:38:30,190 --> 00:38:31,150
During the entire time,

778
00:38:31,150 --> 00:38:32,920
do not contact anyone.

779
00:38:33,590 --> 00:38:34,030
Got it.

780
00:38:34,320 --> 00:38:35,180
Repeat it then.

781
00:38:35,760 --> 00:38:37,220
I must not contact anyone.

782
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:41,480
Uncle,

783
00:38:42,150 --> 00:38:44,510
we're bringing only one bianzhong piece
for the buyer to check.

784
00:38:44,510 --> 00:38:46,480
Is there anything odd about this buyer?

785
00:38:46,480 --> 00:38:47,540
In doing business,

786
00:38:48,530 --> 00:38:50,510
I never present all the goods first.

787
00:38:50,510 --> 00:38:52,420
Buyers have to pay up
before examining the goods.

788
00:38:52,420 --> 00:38:54,920
I'll give you your pay
once the money arrives.

789
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:56,000
In half an hour,

790
00:38:56,670 --> 00:38:58,070
the piece you're holding

791
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,740
and the other 8 in the truck

792
00:38:59,870 --> 00:39:01,590
will be gathered as a complete set

793
00:39:01,590 --> 00:39:02,850
and given to the buyer.

794
00:39:03,030 --> 00:39:04,150
This is my rule.

795
00:39:05,630 --> 00:39:06,890
How thoughtful of you.

796
00:39:08,510 --> 00:39:09,880
This is a very big deal.

797
00:39:10,440 --> 00:39:12,670
There are so many connections to grease,

798
00:39:12,670 --> 00:39:14,150
and so many buddies to pay.

799
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:17,540
You promised to give me 800,000 yuan.

800
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:19,050
Then how do you make money?

801
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:22,930
You think I'm doing this for money?

802
00:39:27,670 --> 00:39:30,330
I've been in this line of business
my whole life.

803
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:33,350
I just can't leave it.

804
00:39:36,630 --> 00:39:37,280
Time to set out!

805
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:37,670
Okay.

806
00:39:55,210 --> 00:40:01,500
[Baoku Fresh Produce Delivery Center]

807
00:40:11,710 --> 00:40:12,510
Drive slower.

808
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:14,660
[Baoku Fresh Produce]
